{"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Enumeration Case","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"}],"externalID":"c:@E@MLNTextWritingMode@MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","title":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","symbolKind":"case"},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":[" If a text's language supports horizontal writing mode, symbols with point"," placement would be laid out horizontally."]}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"]]},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodehorizontal"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal":{"abstract":[],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodehorizontal","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","type":"topic","title":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The property allows control over a symbol’s orientation. Note that the property"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"values act as a hint, so that a symbol whose language doesn’t support the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided orientation will be laid out in its natural orientation. Example:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"English point symbol will be rendered horizontally even if array value contains"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single ‘vertical’ enum value. The order of elements in an array define priority"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"order for the placement of an orientation variant."}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingMode","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode","title":"MLNTextWritingMode","role":"symbol"}}}